Privacy Policy – AI Video Generator
At SoraGPT, we are committed to protecting the privacy and security of our users. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard the information you provide when using our AI-powered video creation app. By using SoraGPT, you consent to the practices described in this policy.
Information We Collect 1.1 Personal Information: When you create an account or subscribe to our Premium Subscription, we may collect personal information such as your name, email address, and payment details. This information is used to provide you with the services you request and to communicate with you about your account.
1.2 User-Generated Content: When you use SoraGPT to create videos, we may collect and store the text prompts, images, and videos you generate. This content is used to improve our AI models and provide you with a better user experience.
1.3 Usage Information: We may collect information about how you use SoraGPT, including your interactions with the app, the features you use, and the videos you create. This information helps us understand how our app is being used and identify areas for improvement.
How We Use Your Information 2.1 Providing and Improving Our Services: We use the information we collect to provide, maintain, and improve SoraGPT, including developing new features and enhancing the user experience.
2.2 Communication: We may use your email address to send you updates about your account, subscription, and new features or products we think you may be interested in. You can opt-out of these communications at any time.
2.3 Aggregated and Anonymized Data: We may aggregate and anonymize user data for analytical purposes, such as improving our AI models and understanding user behavior. This data will not be used to identify individual users.
Information Sharing and Disclosure 3.1 Third-Party Service Providers: We may share your information with trusted third-party service providers who assist us in operating SoraGPT, such as payment processors and cloud storage providers. These providers are obligated to maintain the confidentiality and security of your information.
3.2 Legal Requirements: We may disclose your information if required to do so by law or in response to a valid legal request, such as a court order or government investigation.
Data Security We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
Your Rights and Choices You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information at any time. You can also disable auto-renew for your Premium Subscription and manage your communication preferences within the app settings.
Children’s Privacy SoraGPT is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we become aware that we have collected personal information from a child under 13, we will take steps to delete the information as soon as possible.
Changes to This Privacy Policy We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy within the app and updating the “Last Updated” date at the top of this page.
Contact Us If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, please contact us at info@viralailtd.com.
Last Updated: 5.10.2024